<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Inception!</h1>
  <%= image_tag("banner3.png") %>
  <p>Inception is a web application created at Tel Aviv AngelHack 2012 by Lior Kirsch and Zvika Rap.<br />
  Our goal is to help fashion designers to promote their designs, by embedding them right inside customers facebook photos.</p>
</div>
